description: This file declares the interface for the Bwrm File Manager Object in the Broadway Web Resource Manager implementation, including function prototypes for creating, removing, enrolling, and initializing file manager objects.

methods.name: BwrmCreateFileManager
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Bwrm File Manager object with specified context handles.

methods.name: BwrmFmoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Bwrm File Manager object with specified context handles.

methods.name: BwrmFmoRemove
methods.description: Removes the specified Bwrm File Manager object.

methods.name: BwrmFmoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls required objects into the Bwrm File Manager object.

methods.name: BwrmFmoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Bwrm File Manager object.
